list.name: Default
list.comment: - redesigned sudoku field, empty fields are now empty (SudokuNumberSpinner) - renamed mFocusListener to SudokuFocusListener - fixed Swing bugs on Windows - right border not working - setOpaque(false) for TextField wasn't working as expected

task.summary: - created Git project - created basic class structure - added test method for SudokuSolver in Main.java
- implemented full depth-first search (DFS) algorithm for the sudokus - added tester for CompSudoku - added computational sudoku class (CompSudoku)
- implemented Las Vegas algorithm for terminal pattern creation

- implemented generator for easy and extremly easy - added some more comments - added some more information provided by Level enum - added more variables and edited some function for better sudoku style flexibility - tester method in Main for SudokuGen - added class that for easier use of SudokuGen (StaticGenerator) - added class to improve performance on boolean array (CanBeDugList)
- fixed bug in Las Vegas Algorithm that would push itself into an infinity loop - added full functionality for Evil, Hard and Medium graded sudokus
- added Sudoku Propagations - Added more comments
- added more comments. YEAH!!!!! -.- - added new Class ValueFormatException to describe the most common exception better.
- rollback of CompSudoku to working version.
- added whole Swing GUI - added module GUI
- added live error view - fixed bugs
- added more comments - removed unnecessary code in createUIComponents - generalized SaveHandler class, can now save any image size
